data.description: This beautiful home is set in a cul de sac on the largest lot in this well established subdivision backed up to woods. 1760 sq ft. with a 3 car charge. The home has a huge living room and master bedroom. Split floor plan. The formal dining room is the perfect place to host large dinners. All the bedrooms provide walk-in closets. New roof 2018. New water heater 2021. Call to schedule your private showing today. This one will not last. *Realtors SEE AGENT REMARKS*
